85E7 21 FD               TEQA #0xFD
85E9 2B FF B0            JNE FAIL
85EC 04 A5 02            LDX #0xA502
85EF 13                  DECXL
85F0 2A 1F F3            LDA XH
85F3 21 A5               TEQA #0xA5
85F5 2B FF B0            JNE FAIL
85F8 2A 1F F4            LDA XL
85FB 21 01               TEQA #0x01
85FD 2B FF B0            JNE FAIL
8600 13                  DECXL
8601 2A 1F F3            LDA XH
