8606 2B FF B0            JNE FAIL
8609 2A 1F F4            LDA XL
860C 21 00               TEQA #0x00
860E 2B FF B0            JNE FAIL
8611 13                  DECXL
8612 2A 1F F3            LDA XH
8615 21 A5               TEQA #0xA5
8617 2B FF B0            JNE FAIL
861A 2A 1F F4            LDA XL
861D 21 FF               TEQA #0xFF
861F 2B FF B0            JNE FAIL
8622 13                  DECXL 
8623 2A 1F F3            LDA XH
8626 21 A5               TEQA #0xA5
8628 2B FF B0            JNE FAIL
862B 2A 1F F4            LDA XL
862E 21 FE               TEQA #0xFE
8630 2B FF B0            JNE FAIL
8633 04 00 02            LDX #0x0002 ; Check E status
8636 13                  DECXL
8637 2A 1F FA            LDA EQUAL
863A 21 00               TEQA #0x00
863C 2B FF B0            JNE FAIL
863F 04 00 01            LDX #0x0001
8642 13                  DECXL
8643 2A 1F FA            LDA EQUAL
8646 21 01               TEQA #0x01
8648 2B FF B0            JNE FAIL
864B 04 FF FF            LDX #0xFFFF
864E 13                  DECXL
864F 2A 1F FA            LDA EQUAL
8652 21 00               TEQA #0x00
8654 2B FF B0            JNE FAIL
                         ; --------------------------------------------------------------------
                         ; OP.14  RRC 0x****   Rotate Right Logical Address location through Carry 
                         ;                     C -> b7 b6 b5 b4 b3 b2 b1 b0 -> C  
                         ; --------------------------------------------------------------------
